# Git commits — no Cursor co-author

When creating git commits for this repository:

- Do **not** add `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>` or any Cursor trailer.
- Use `git commit -F message.txt` or `git $(echo commit-tree)` if the environment injects co-author trailers on `git commit`.
- Commit messages should list only the human author (Setegn Worku Alemu).

The site owner does not want Cursor listed as a co-author on GitHub.
